_model: media-kit
---
title: Media Kit
---
body:

Use these assets to promote your involvement with PyCon DE & PyData 2026 — whether you are a speaker, sponsor, volunteer, or community member.

### Downloads

- **[Media Kit (ZIP, 34 MB)](/static/mediakit/PyConDE%20PyData%202026%20Media%20Kit%202026-03.zip)** — logos, Python illustrations, and example templates
- **[Brand Manual (PDF, 1.7 MB)](/static/mediakit/PyConDE%20PyData%202026%20Media%20Kit%20Manual.pdf)** — colors, typography, logo usage rules, and contrast guidelines

Please read the brand manual before using any assets to ensure consistent and correct usage of the PyCon DE & PyData branding.
